{"tid":505703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角現神秘富婆當街派錢 富婆：等大家開心過聖誕","createTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T04:30:29.000Z","uid":39539,"like":263,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ba61f5db47022c6ef1004c9c41e88497a5e8d4","tid":505703,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"旺角女子聲稱唔開心，當街向途人派錢。下午4時許，一名女子在廣東道1047號向途人派發紙幣，並透露「唔開心」及「想搵地方跳樓」，途人擔心會出事，於是報警。警員接報後於附近兜截，在亞皆老街與深圳街交界找到涉事女子，當時她身上孭著一個斜孭袋，內有一大疊現金，由於她情緒激動，警方遂將她帶到公園安頓及查問，同時召來救護車戒備，經調查後相信事件無可疑，女子拒絕送院，由警員及救護員護送步行返附近寓所。現場消息指，女子已派出至少數萬港元現金，她亦透露早前與女兒「嗌交」，未知是否與派錢事件有關。 <br />\n<br />\n據附近一家找換店的職員透露，涉事女子疑是區內街坊，不時見到她出入，今午5時許見她於現場出現，不停來回踱步，並拿出港幣及人民幣現金，問途人「要唔要呀？」然後塞到對方手中，有途人被嚇呆，亦有人收下現金後離開。其後有警察到場調查，在找換店對開發現該女子，並向她查問事情始末，但她全程神情呆滯，警員遂將她帶到亞皆老街與塘尾道交界一個公園詳細查問。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，派錢女子姓張，與丈夫已離異，現獨自照顧正在讀小學的女兒。張婦透露，女兒成績一般，現就讀一間band 2學校，惟她希望女兒能夠入讀band 1學校，故加倍催谷，女兒疑因此感到壓力過大而反抗，致兩母女近日曾多番拗撬，關係轉差，張婦更聲稱曾被女兒打。受母女之間的問題困擾，張婦表示感到相當「唔開心」，於是當街派錢擬「等途人開心吓」，她自稱由下午起已派出數萬港元。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171221/mobile/bkn-20171221184556946-1221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171221%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171221184556946-1221_00822_001.html&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7bb28469\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171221/mobile/bkn-20171221184556946-1221_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/195850_d9be806158167741d90e9619136286a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F195850_d9be806158167741d90e9619136286a7.jpg&h=bc92503e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/195851_dc154f6a33c4d8c752a51ae67889e29f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F195851_dc154f6a33c4d8c752a51ae67889e29f.jpg&h=cbc5af7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fab0ab629040687e9e8b955d9f0e30eba76e69d","tid":505703,"uid":106589,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfa3e9fd6d622f0507459822dacfe3c13d5fb8b","tid":505703,"uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c656bfb88b43ef52bda09ec1018f0dc74c1ed3d4","tid":505703,"uid":77484,"like":490,"dislike":3,"score":487,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ae9d7d225cd9272180d6fea33e77dc95e1f9fa","tid":505703,"uid":34714,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"咁細疊!"},{"pid":"8e0d459d3b9ad570616d4dfcada7fdb17b871ea8","tid":505703,"uid":37197,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"咁有錢 做我繼母喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34722fa93a09da6a4613572d21f0ef2c376f8bf","tid":505703,"uid":2583,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"龍咁威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58e4678336852abcd41215124a80e34abb52484","tid":505703,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":42,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"有人仔滲咗係入面，不了"},{"pid":"bc21cfe0f150f7d445766b82f5f7e56a8f3617c8","tid":505703,"uid":1255,"like":291,"dislike":4,"score":287,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"派到黎真係唔知收唔收好<img src=\"/assets/